# =============================================================================
# Usage Instructions
# =============================================================================

# 1. Copy this file to your React project root
# 2. Rename to .env.local (for local development) or .env (for deployment)
# 3. Update REACT_APP_MEMORY_API_BASE_URL for your environment
# 4. Set REACT_APP_MEMORY_API_KEY with your actual API key
# 5. Configure persona IDs to match your application's personas
# 6. Enable/disable features based on your requirements
# 7. Adjust performance settings based on your usage patterns
# 8. Set debug mode to true during development for detailed logging

# Note: All environment variables starting with REACT_APP_ will be available
# in your React application. Never expose sensitive information like API keys
# in client-side code in production environments.
